<div id="moneyInOutModal" class="modal hidden">
    <div class="modal-content md:modal-content-sm">
        <div class="modal-header">
            <h2 class="text-2xl text-slate-gray-700 font-semibold">{{ i18n.trans('till-session-cash-movments') }}</h2>
            <button class="btn btn-icon btn-danger ml-2" data-toggle="modal" data-target="moneyInOutModal">
                <i class="fa fw fa-times"></i>
            </button>
        </div>
        <div class="modal-body">
            <form id="cashMovmentForm" method="POST">
                <input type="hidden" name="action" value="cash-movment">
                <input type="hidden" name="token" value="{{ fsc.getNewToken() }}">
                <p>Ingrese la cantidad a retirar/depositar. Utilize signo <em>negativo</em> <strong>&minus;</strong> si es un retiro.</p>
                <div class="form-group mt-4">
                    <span class="text-xl font-medium text-left">{{ i18n.trans('amount') }}</span>
                    <input name="amount" type="number" required>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group mt-2">
                    <span class="text-xl font-medium text-left">{{ i18n.trans('description') }}</span>
                    <input name="description" type="text" required>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
        <div class="modal-footer">
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-warning btn-round" id="cashMovmentSaveButton" data-action="moneyInOutAction"
                    data-toggle="modal" data-target="moneyInOutModal">
                {{ i18n.trans('continue') }}</button>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
